attributes.description: Note: for each run the maximum number of input/output records and bytes across its stages is selected. The totals represent the sum for all selected runs. Such approach is applicable for batch jobs reading/writing data in one stage (common for ETL). It may result in error for streaming applications or the applications which read/write data multiple times during its execution.
attributes.title: Totals
